<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>إِلَى سَيِّدِ الْخَلْقِ وَحَبِيبِ الْحَقِّ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>صَاحِبِ الْخُلُقِ الْعَظِيمِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>رَحْمَةُ اللهِ لِلْعَالَمِينَ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>سَيِّدِنَا مُحَمَّدٍ بْنِ عَبْدِ اللهِ - صلى الله عليه وسلم -<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>